    "description": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">At the start of your turn during a conflict, if you are driving your </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>personal vehicle</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">, you may spend <strong>@LOSS[10 mp].</strong> If you do, choose one option: the next time you deal damage during this turn, deal </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>【</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>SL × 2</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>】 </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">extra damage; </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>or</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">, the next time you suffer damage before the start of your next turn, that damage is reduced by </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>【</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>SL × 2</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>】</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">(applied </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>before</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">damage Affinities); </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>or</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">, you recover from a status effect of your choice among </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>slow</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">and </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>weak</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">.</span></p>",
